  Description: "He joined for powder pay, not for banners. An ignition flare scorched
    his face; eyelids blistered shut. He doesn\u2019t want pity \u2014 just darkness
    that doesn\u2019t burn.\n\nTreatment: Cool cloth with water and wine. Lay dressings
    over closed eyes; never peel, only replace. Apply poultice to cheeks. Blindness
    is likely.\n\nRequires: 4 Bandages"
